sequenceDiagram
  participant IRQ as irq_ctrl/periph
  participant HU as Hazard Unit
  participant CPU as cpu core
  participant RF as Regfile
  participant PCN as PC Next

  IRQ->>HU: i_irq_take=1
  HU-->>CPU: accept_irq=1 only when !mem_wait
  CPU->>RF: write lr (r14) <= pc-2
  CPU->>PCN: select irq_vector
  CPU-->>CPU: flush younger state (IF/ID and ID/EX)
  Note over CPU: IRQ accepted at instruction boundary
